v1.0.0 - Initial Release

YXX Comment Commander Pro — A professional comment management plugin.
Features

Per-post/page control (with a "Comment Control" sidebar on the edit screen)
Bulk enable/disable comments
One-click deletion of all comments (irreversible, use with caution)
Hide comments from guest visitors
Installation
Download the zip file
WordPress Dashboard → Plugins → Add New → Upload Plugin
After activation, navigate to Settings → Comment Commander Pro and enter your Creem License Key
Notes
Requires PHP 7.4+ and WordPress 5.5+
A valid Creem License Key is required to activate Pro features
Automatic updates check for new versions via the GitHub API
